item.title: Lax
item.description: I haven’t added any entries in awhile.. I have been sorta busy. I have a new class, Data structures. Fun Fun… programming and such.. but whatever. I have been hanging a lot with Kinnera.. i enjoy that. Its nice. I hope to have a very good block. I imagine i will. it seems to be going well. It is very exciting so far. and it only seems to be able to go upwards… well.
